import {
  Box,
  Card,
  CardBody,
  CardHeader,
  Center,
  Heading,
  Stack,
  StackDivider,
  Text,
  Image,
  VStack,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import React from "react";

const Landing = () => {
  return (
    <Center h="100vh" flexDir="column" w="100vw">
      <Card align="center" rounded="2xl" h="xl" w="md" p="1">
        <CardHeader
          w="full"
          background="radial-gradient(40% 80% at top, #fde68a -80%, white 100%)"
        >
          <Image
            position="absolute"
            left="50%"
            right="50%"
            alt="logo"
            boxSize="10px"
            src="home-ui-bg.svg"
          />
          <VStack gap={3}>
            <Image
              bgGradient="linear(to-b, #fcd34d , #fffbeb)"
              alt="logo"
              boxSize="80px"
              rounded="full"
              src="logo192.png"
              py="2"
            />
            <Heading size="md">Welcome</Heading>
            <Text fontSize="sm">Please enter your details to sign in</Text>
          </VStack>
        </CardHeader>

        <CardBody>
          <Stack divider={<StackDivider />} spacing="4">
            <Box>
              <Heading size="xs" textTransform="uppercase">
                Summary
              </Heading>
              <Text pt="2" fontSize="sm">
                View a summary of all your clients over the last month.
              </Text>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Heading size="xs" textTransform="uppercase">
                Overview
              </Heading>
              <Text pt="2" fontSize="sm">
                Check out the overview of your clients.
              </Text>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Heading size="xs" textTransform="uppercase">
                Analysis
              </Heading>
              <Text pt="2" fontSize="sm">
                See a detailed analysis of all your business clients.
              </Text>
            </Box>
          </Stack>
        </CardBody>
      </Card>
    </Center>
  );
};

export default Landing;
